{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"lcvk4gxd3rvf6dtcuzh2j4q","title":"Refutability","desc":"","updated":1671034421383,"created":1671033821979,"custom":{},"fname":"programing.rust.Patterns-and-Matching.Refutability","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"50e93d09a7d7b5199698b63e5b7d1463","links":[],"anchors":{"refutability-whether-a-pattern-might-fail-to-match":{"type":"header","text":"Refutability: Whether a Pattern Might fail to Match","value":"refutability-whether-a-pattern-might-fail-to-match","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"translate":{"type":"header","text":"Translate","value":"translate","line":24,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"cz07ovuehwn4h16op3j6dho","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"refutability\">Refutability<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#refutability\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"refutability-whether-a-pattern-might-fail-to-match\">Refutability: Whether a Pattern Might fail to Match<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#refutability-whether-a-pattern-might-fail-to-match\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/ch18-02-refutability.html\">https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/ch18-02-refutability.html</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>Patterns come in 2 forms:\n<ul>\n<li>refutable: Patterns that can <strong>fail to match for some possible value</strong>.</li>\n<li>inrrefutable: Patterns that will <strong>match for any possible value passed</strong> </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Irrefutable patterns\n<ul>\n<li><code>let</code> statements</li>\n<li><code>for</code> loops</li>\n<li>function parameters</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Refutable (with compiler warns) &#x26; irrefutable \n<ul>\n<li><code>if let</code></li>\n<li><code>while let</code> </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>match</code> arms must be refutable patterns, except for the last arm (any remaining values with an irrefutable pattern)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"translate\">Translate<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#translate\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Refute /rɪˈfyut/: có thể bác bỏ (refute something to prove that something is wrong)</li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"xfkxbponh0sohobo6pual15","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1668137379975,"created":1663481872547,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"docs"},"contentHash":"cb44915142ec96bef8f764f3dc90389e","links":[],"anchors":{"welcome-to-my-page":{"type":"header","text":"Welcome to my page","value":"welcome-to-my-page","line":7,"column":0,"depth":1},"contacts":{"type":"header","text":"Contacts","value":"contacts","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"dendron":{"type":"header","text":"Dendron","value":"dendron","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["u5a2e2vvfn3x7k0shuvmb1b","qw8y69zxn8wr7tzz4gtcrrv","q7qw45jglqwmynary64q67c","6wjqcjgkrpeqtmzb1o8o1q8","3ervbn5we7t8v2l2vwtx847","4qi2z0z9fquupbd651xausx","sencgim78q74o1zuyvy1vz7","ue4oml1si982t3mmbthyxi9","zrogwjgtze8ne5joqpz8ty9","oesia0lbzh03fsoy124ck0k","el3p9zjue6h3b6zsl9oejkt","t5grkmcwvu4nl43igsj4gxz"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"# Welcome to my page\n\n- This is a place where I write my knowledge in both Vietnamese and English.\n- Please feel free to correct me if there is anything not right.\n\n## Contacts\n\n- [Github](https://github.com/thanhpp)\n- [Discord](https://discord.gg/ugNRjFNqjp)\n- [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/thanhpp/)\n\n## Dendron\n\n- [Home Page](https://wiki.dendron.so/)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"alwaysPrompt","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMar